{"tid":1330840,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[2019書展] 三中商？不了。","createTime":"2019-07-18T17:13:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T03:27:37.000Z","uid":212365,"like":13,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"368077b952fe8721e4100ecdfb890755277e9f11","tid":1330840,"uid":212365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:13:50.000Z","msg":"一年一度嘅書展又黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n呢到多左咁多uncle auntie 相信你地都會帶啲仔女去行下買下書咁(補充練習就唔好喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />) <br />\n而家香港咁亂咁緊張去下行書展唔緊要 但緊記<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">抵制三中商！！</span></span><br />\n三中商係咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢地係三聯書店、中華書局同商務嘅代稱。而呢三間大型連鎖書店已經係多年前被揭發係由中聯辦直接持有！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n意味著中共暗中操控住文化傳播，係你揀書睇前佢已經幫你揀左先！<br />\n<br />\n三中商全部隸屬於聯合出版集團<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />佢地唔單單話唔比你本書係佢舖頭賣，更加控制埋出版同物流，只要你本書比佢地定義為「敏感」你就唔使指意可以係佢地到出書<br />\n而「敏感」嘅書籍絕對唔單指政治書籍，一啲比較開放嘅議題例如同性戀、LGBTQ嘅書籍都有可能不被出版。<br />\n同場加映：寫BL小說遭判監10年 網民批刑罰過重<br />\n<a href=\"https://china.hket.com/article/2211091/%E5%AF%ABBL%E5%B0%8F%E8%AA%AA%E9%81%AD%E5%88%A4%E7%9B%A310%E5%B9%B4%20%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%89%B9%E5%88%91%E7%BD%B0%E9%81%8E%E9%87%8D\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fchina.hket.com%2Farticle%2F2211091%2F%25E5%25AF%25ABBL%25E5%25B0%258F%25E8%25AA%25AA%25E9%2581%25AD%25E5%2588%25A4%25E7%259B%25A310%25E5%25B9%25B4%2520%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591%25E6%2589%25B9%25E5%2588%2591%25E7%25BD%25B0%25E9%2581%258E%25E9%2587%258D&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHE%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=7046a94a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://china.hket.com/article/2211091/%E5%AF%ABBL%E5%B0%8F%E8%AA%AA%E9%81%AD%E5%88%A4%E7%9B%A310%E5%B9%B4%20%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91%E6%89%B9%E5%88%91%E7%BD%B0%E9%81%8E%E9%87%8D</a><br />\n無錯，係中國就係連出一本講同性戀嘅書都可以比人拉去坐監。中共係香港當然唔會咁大膽，就係靠呢啲軟性嘅控制，令到我地慢慢接觸講大中華嘅書多左，控制我地嘅思想同言論。最可怕嘅係，我地可能唔會察覺<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">咁對我地有咩影響？</span><br />\n第一，佢危害到香港嘅出版自由。<br />\n不少作家嘅書因為題材被定義為敏感就未能出版，而三中商佔香港約一半的零售網絡，缺少呢啲零售點，呢啲作家同獨立出版商都非常難經營。<br />\n第二，佢踐踏緊一國兩制。<br />\n暗地裡插手我地嘅出版同文化交流，無疑係扼殺緊香港人嘅核心價值， 踐踏思想自由。<br />\n第三，代表緊我地送緊錢比中共洗呀！！<br />\n屌你老母！助長班仆街！文化係軟實力呀！<br />\n<br />\n想了解多啲三中商背後嘅運作同手段推介你睇呢段鏗鏘集<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<a href=\"http://m.liberalstudies.hk/video/programme.php?vid=tcs18-1753\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.liberalstudies.hk%2Fvideo%2Fprogramme.php%3Fvid%3Dtcs18-1753&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHE%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=a35806ff\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://m.liberalstudies.hk/video/programme.php?vid=tcs18-1753</a><br />\n<br />\n其實香港仲有好多獨立嘅書店又好多唔同種類嘅書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />加上小店比起大集團難經營 希望大家都可以支持下本地嘅書店同創作啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一嚟抵制紅色滲透 二嚟支持小店<br />\n以下開放討論有咩香港書店值得推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家多啲幫襯"},{"pid":"88b81704f7ae5c4c674722545bb91bf4567e30c1","tid":1330840,"uid":212365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:14:28.000Z","msg":"我冇野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/yo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9ad4d4be72678dda9f7fe4afe712b25cba9c5c48","tid":1330840,"uid":212365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:14:42.000Z","msg":"我有權唔解鎖電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/photo.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59b6d48e9ab26f54f17467b33a81e0aeb2f3e292","tid":1330840,"uid":212365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:15:09.000Z","msg":"我唔會簽<img src=\"/as