n你唔好叫埋差佬黎捉人？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個唔清楚<br />\n不過眾志有人去示威 冇比人趕走<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/352779/%E6%9B%B8%E5%B1%952019-%E6%9B%B8%E5%B1%95%E6%8F%AD%E5%B9%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E5%88%B0-%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%95%86-%E6%AA%94%E4%BD%8D%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F352779%2F%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%25B1%25952019-%25E6%259B%25B8%25E5%25B1%2595%25E6%258F%25AD%25E5%25B9%2595-%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E7%259C%25BE%25E5%25BF%2597%25E6%2588%2590%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%2588%25B0-%25E4%25B8%2589%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%2595%2586-%25E6%25AA%2594%25E4%25BD%258D%25E6%258A%2597%25E8%25AD%25B0&d=mJB0HZfowtkqKRKkSYSHE%2FaDgzkAO6tKN2FhpyhCcE0%3D&h=ecd2c7cc\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/352779/%E6%9B%B8%E5%B1%952019-%E6%9B%B8%E5%B1%95%E6%8F%AD%E5%B9%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E7%9C%BE%E5%BF%97%E6%88%90%E5%93%A1%E5%88%B0-%E4%B8%89%E4%B8%AD%E5%95%86-%E6%AA%94%E4%BD%8D%E6%8A%97%E8%AD%B0</a>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:58:43.000Z","msg":"第一日去果陣見到佢<br />\n見到有好多人係三中商買書, 唔知d人係因為唔知三中商係咩定係覺得唔關佢事"},{"pid":"ec2ae6351ab56cf973de77b1deb87f4165be3adb","tid":1330840,"uid":69525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:59:00.000Z","msg":"如果大家去書展既話順便做埋文宣！<br />\n咁多人流 慢慢send<br />\n<br />\n人人都可以做文宣<br />\n善用Airdrop<br />\n 首先 設定&gt;一般&gt;關於本機 改個靚名<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Q1vJw5M.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FQ1vJw5M.png&h=75f30bb8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n再揀圖send出去 <br />\n重點強調 20/7沒有任何遊行 同 <br />\n大大力宣傳21/7 改返做維園為集合點 <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HRpRFZy.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHRpRFZy.png&h=f04a049e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5ORsYMd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5ORsYMd.png&h=1456c573&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/CYH7YMe.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FCYH7YMe.png&h=5e0d2be9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8cvhBxU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8cvhBxU.png&h=ee07484f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/h15hBxV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fh15hBxV.png&h=69a8630b&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"07ab443b8bf549af15bd78aea62134c739af2867","tid":1330840,"uid":198461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:59:27.000Z","msg":"借位推文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n[ 香城Online 國戰 -- 戰略及建設新中國篇 ] ---永遠置頂，全世界入黎 !<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1330226\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1330226</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"de4206fb4e9e32b085306604e90386222edd4208","tid":1330840,"uid":123827,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"e2c787eb5d92aa0629b47e0039a9eb7c83a35237","tid":1330840,"uid":206417,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa184cdb856f8dd626aae600416e5dfca0502a38","tid":1330840,"uid":212365,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8d15efc94aa6516deabe32aa32ecea8bc81420a4","tid":1330840,"uid":216364,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:15:45.000Z","msg":"幫推 好似話佢哋書展檔增加咗保安見到有人示威會請人離開<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你唔好叫埋差佬黎捉人？"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-18T17:50:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />呢個唔清楚<br />\n不過眾志有人去示威 冇比人趕走<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/352779/%E6%9B%B8%E5%B1%952019-%E6%9B%B8%E5%B1%95%E6%8F%AD%E5%B9%95-%E9%A6%99%E6%B